sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Customer
  participant App as Customer App
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant Map as Map / OSRM
  participant Pricing as Pricing Service
  participant Redis as Redis Cache
  participant AI as AI Service
  Customer->>App: Enter pickup, destination, vehicle type
  App->>Gateway: GET /api/pricing/estimate
  Gateway->>Map: Normalize address and route
  Map-->>Gateway: Coordinates, distance, duration
  Gateway->>Pricing: EstimateFare(route, vehicleType, time)
  Pricing->>Redis: Read surge and cached quote
  Redis-->>Pricing: Surge/cache data
  Pricing->>AI: Predict ETA and surge support
  alt AI responds within timeout
    AI-->>Pricing: Prediction result
  else AI timeout or disabled
    Pricing->>Pricing: Use rule-based fallback
  end
  Pricing->>Pricing: Calculate fare and quote TTL
  Pricing->>Redis: Cache quote
  Pricing-->>Gateway: Fare, ETA, distance, surge
  Gateway-->>App: Quote response
  App-->>Customer: Display estimated fare
